creator: Quincy Media, Inc.
descriptionHtml: WXOW News 19 is La Crosse's Own. We are your local source for news that's important to you. The WXOW news app provides live streaming video, breaking news, and detailed, up-to-the-minute weather forecasts to help you plan your activities. With your approval, our app alerts will let you know about big stories and weather events as they happen. We also bring you the latest sports scores and stories from local high school, college, and the pros. Connect with us and the community through our Facebook and Twitter feeds.
descriptionShort: The WXOW News 19 app is from LaCrosse's local source of news important to you.
